usage.title: local file list
usage.header: Directory listing of your local filesystem

optional.name: -A
optional.docs: List all entries except for . and ..

optional.name: -a
optional.docs: Include directory entries whose names begin with a dot (.)

optional.name: -d
optional.docs: Directories are listed as plain files

optional.name: -c
optional.docs: Use time when file status was last changed for sorting

optional.name: -t
optional.docs: Sort by time modified (most recently modified first)
